cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DB 

Reasoning: 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on improving retrieval functionalities of clinical decision support systems. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is also likely as the paper deals with semantic relations between concepts extracted from medical documents. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are possible categories as the paper discusses using informative power to improve retrieval functionalities. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is a possible category as the paper deals with extracting semantic relations from medical documents.
